sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Auckland

sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Adelaide
sky.tennis.uk.description: Mirra Andreeva, the Indian Wells champion, faces Canadian Open winner Victoria Mboko in a teenage showdown for the Adelaide crown. Both are looking to clinch a first WTA 500 title. (17.01)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Itchy and Scratchy: The Movie: While Homer and Marge are at parents' evening, Bart breaks the babysitter's teeth. So Homer vows never to let him see the Itchy and Scratchy film. (S4 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge Gets a Job: When Marge gets a job at the power plant, Mr Burns falls in love with her and invites her over to dinner, complete with a kidnapped Tom Jones to serenade them. (S4 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: New Kid on the Block: When Homer gets kicked out of an all-you-can-eat seafood restaurant for eating too much, he takes the owner to court. (S4 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa's First Word: The family try to get Maggie to say her first word. But Homer's glad that she hasn't spoken yet, because all Lisa and Bart do is talk back to him. (S4 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Triple Bypass: Homer has a heart attack while he's watching TV. The hospital says he needs a bypass, but Homer can't afford it. Of course, there's always Dr Nick... (S4 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Selma's Choice: After Homer gets sick from a giant sandwich he's been eating for months, Selma steps in to take the kids to a new alcohol-based theme park. (S4 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: O Brother, Where Bart Thou?: Bart grows jealous of Lisa's relationship with Maggie and heads to an orphanage to find a baby brother. Guest starring Kim Cattrall. (S21 Ep8/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Thursdays with Abie: Grampa tells a journalist about his wartime service on a battleship. The story brings Grampa lots of attention, but his relationship with Homer suffers. (S21 Ep9/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Once Upon a Time in Springfield: Krusty gets a beautiful new co-star (guest voice Anne Hathaway). Mr Burns withdraws the staff's free doughnuts at the nuclear power plant. (S21 Ep10/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Million Dollar Maybe: Homer wins the lottery jackpot but has to keep it secret from the family. Guest starring Chris Martin from Coldplay. (S21 Ep11/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Boy Meets Curl: When Homer takes Marge out for a romantic evening at the ice rink, they become hooked on curling and end up competing to reach the Winter Olympics. (S21 Ep12/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: From Susie Dent to Miquita Oliver and Bez, what do our top celebs think of Cocaine Bear, Glastonbury and much more? Oh, and Ricky Tomlinson, Sue Johnston and Antiques Roadshow. (S5 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's Asia, The Day of the Jackal and Married at First Sight UK this time on the 'Box. Also, The Chase Celebrity Special, Love Triangle Australia and James May and the Dull Men. (S24 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Strictly Come Dancing, Married at First Sight UK and Rivals are on this time. Plus Antiques Roadshow, Love Triangle Australia, Ambulance, Countdown and ITV News (Trump). (S24 Ep10) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gym-bunny James arrives for his date with his mum in tow. Fiona and Craig bond over shared life experiences. Can supernatural fiction writer Tracey lift Sairaphina's spirits? (S13 Ep3) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welsh hairdresser Jess wants a man who's a cut above the rest. Charity shop manager Casey has his dream white wedding all mapped out. But is his date husband material? (S13 Ep6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's Asia, The Day of the Jackal and Married at First Sight UK this time on the 'Box. Also, The Chase Celebrity Special, Love Triangle Australia and James May and the Dull Men. (S24 Ep9) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Strictly Come Dancing, Married at First Sight UK and Rivals are on this time. Plus Antiques Roadshow, Love Triangle Australia, Ambulance, Countdown and ITV News (Trump). (S24 Ep10) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mixing Bowl: Bijou New York diner The Mixing Bowl is haemorrhaging money thanks to manager Mike's out-of-control marketing plans. Can Gordon get things back on track? (S1 Ep2) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Seascape: Gordon Ramsay visits the Seascape restaurant in the seaside village of Islip, on Long Island in New York, where owner Peter has nearly a million dollars of debt. (S1 Ep3) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks Omnibus
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sienna and Cleo's relationship is still fragile. Ant finds himself in hot water. Old friends return to help lift Donny's spirits. And a revenge plot closes in on one resident.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister that features a variety of cats doing strange things, some soldiers stuck in the sand and a dog balancing on a rope.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Winner Winner Turkey Dinner: Jay's Thanksgiving toast honours the entire family on their recent successes, even though everyone knows that they aren't quite true. (S9 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brushes with Celebrity: The Pritchett-Dunphy-Tucker clan recount their celebrity encounters. When Phil shows a house to his musical hero, he's determined to make a good impression. (S9 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Tough Love: After leaving his real estate firm to strike out on his own, Phil decides that a solo camping trip in the wild is just what he needs to boost his confidence. (S9 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: He Said, She Shed: The homeowners association deny Claire's request to build a 'She Shed' in the garden, and only Luke and Phil know the real reason why. (S9 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dear Beloved Family: Gloria rushes Phil to hospital for emergency surgery when he experiences intense stomach pains. (S9 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Don't Tell the Bride
E4Plus1.uk.description: The One with All the Pixies: Sam has £13k to spend on his pixie wedding to his love, Luanne. Will Luanne, who dreams of a traditional service, appreciate his scheme?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Don't Tell the Bride
E4Plus1.uk.description: The One with the Dinosaurs: Elle has her heart set on a classy wedding at Liverpool's iconic Liver Building. But Phil plans a big day to go down in history.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lela's: In California, Gordon Ramsay visits Lela's, a fine dining restaurant run by inexperienced owner Lela and young chef Ricky. Can Gordon save them from complete disaster? (S1 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sebastian's: Gordon Ramsay visits Sebastian's, a pizzeria in Los Angeles. The customers are scarce and the debt is mounting. Can Gordon turn the restaurant's fortunes around? (S1 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Finn McCool's: Gordon Ramsay visits Finn McCool's, a traditional Irish pub in the Hamptons, where the family feuding has got out of hand. Can Gordon mediate? (S1 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Olde Stone Mill: Gordon Ramsay visits The Olde Stone Mill in Tuckahoe, New York. The restaurant has been restored, but owner Dean can't get customers through the door. (S1 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brother from the Same Planet: When Homer is late picking up Bart from a school football game, Bart gets a surrogate dad from an agency. (S4 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Love Lisa: On Valentine's Day, Lisa takes pity on Ralph and gives him a card. But when he falls in love with her, it leads to a bitter feud between their families. (S4 Ep15/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Duffless: Homer fails a breathalyser test while driving home from the Duff brewery and has to quit drinking for a month. (S4 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: So It Has Come to This: The Simpsons' Clip Show: Bart's special April Fools' Day prank seriously misfires when the whole house explodes. (S4 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Sister Act
E4Plus1.uk.description: (1992) Comedy starring Whoopi Goldberg. A casino singer who witnesses a Mob murder goes into hiding at a convent, where she soon has the choir rocking. With Maggie Smith.

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Homer and Her Sisters: A self-help expert prompts Homer to do something unthinkable: get to know Patty and Selma. (S36 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - The Man Who Flew Too Much: Homer's old bowling team, the Pin Pals, reunite. But disaster befalls them on their helicopter ride to the state championships. (S36 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Angel Has Fallen
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Action-thriller sequel. Secret agent Mike Banning (Gerard Butler) goes on the run when he's framed for an attack on the President. Can he clear his name?

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Citroen: Will and Gus take on a Citroen BX with no brakes, bad paintwork and a rodent infestation - and they've got five days to fix it and flog it. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Alfa Romeo: Gus and Will hunt down an affordable Italian car, and eventually find an Alfa Romeo 155 hiding in a barn. Making space for an inspection proves a challenge. S1 Ep5

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Porsche: Will and Gus buy a Porsche 923 with a cracked interior, bad paintwork and ripped seats. This driving legend is well past its best, but they still hope to turn a profit. S1 Ep6

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Volvo: Will and Gus lay their hands on a potentially very valuable Volvo. It's great to look at, but doesn't start easily and cannot stop. S1 Ep7

UAndYesterday.uk.title: 'Allo 'Allo!
UAndYesterday.uk.description: The Dreaded Circular Saw: Good moaning, I shall say zis only vonce... classic laughs with Rene and co. in the outrageous wartime sitcom. Rene and Leclerc open up Gruber's safe. S5 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.title: 'Allo 'Allo!
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Enter Denise: Rene could be facing a fate worse than life with Edith. The leader of the Communist Resistance recognises him as her childhood sweetheart and vows to marry him. S5 Ep5

UAndYesterday.uk.title: 'Allo 'Allo!
UAndYesterday.uk.description: A Marriage of Inconvenience: Refreshingly un-PC comedy. Rene's friends rally round to try and save him from his impending marriage to the leader of the Communists. S5 Ep6

UAndYesterday.uk.title: 'Allo 'Allo!
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Post-Matrimonial Depression: Bawdy wartime sitcom. More laughs from the French cafe as Rene disguises himself as his father in order to escape the wrath of Denise Laroque. S5 Ep7

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Knottingley to Ripon: On the last leg of his epic journey across the north of England, Robbie tackles the fast-flowing River Ouse and is forced to make an emergency stop. S3 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Sheffield to Keadby: Robbie Cumming makes a running repair to his narrowboat on the Tinsley lock flight in South Yorkshire, then cruises beneath Conisbrough's magnificent viaduct. S4 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Keadby to Kiveton Park: Robbie Cumming tackles the fast-flowing River Trent and is invited to join a night-time illuminated boat parade. S4 Ep2

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Lincoln to Nottingham: Narrowboater Robbie Cumming faces a journey of many challenges as he runs aground and breaks down in Nottingham. S4 Ep3

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Loughborough to Braunston: Robbie Cumming has problems with ice on the Grand Union Canal, and ends his journey in Braunston, Northamptonshire. S4 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Shardlow to Stoke-on-Trent: Robbie Cumming journeys from Shardlow to Etruria Junction, Stoke on Trent, exploring the Trent and Mersey Canal. S1 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Robson Green: World's Most Amazing Walks
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Douro Valley, Portugal: Robson Green walks a beautiful but lesser-known route in the Douro Valley in Northern Portugal, rich in ancient art, wildlife and world-famous wine. S1 Ep5

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Robson Green: World's Most Amazing Walks
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Jurassic Coast, England: Robson explores an ancient trail along the stunning Jurassic Coast in Dorset, and comes face-to-skull with a giant Pliosaur, also known as a 'Sea-Rex'. S1 Ep

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Lotus Esprit/MG TF/ERF Lorry: On the way to pick up two lovely '70s Lotus sports cars, Derek takes to the skies for his first ever helicopter flight in a 1967 Bell 47 chopper. S9 Ep10

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Moskvitch: Dave's drawn to a Fiat Uno 45 in '1970's beige', with 36,000 miles on the clock. S9 Ep11

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Willys Jeep: Tucked away in the showroom is a WW2-era Willys Jeep. Its original condition means there might be a bunfight for a military vehicle that's ripe for restoration. S7 Ep6

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Austin Healey: Up for auction this week is a 1980 Ford Escort, a hand-built 1946 Bedford 12 electric car, and a beautiful, red 1957 Austin Healey. S7 Ep7

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Triumph TR4A: Derek collects a beautifully restored and carefully modified 1936 Wolseley 14/56. Meanwhile, a Batman-inspired Chrysler Crossfire is dropped off at the Thornton le Dale garage. S7 Ep8

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Vauxhall Cresta: Paul's doing the pick-ups in Lancashire where a rare 1960 Vauxhall Cresta PA Friary estate in dusky pink awaits. S7 Ep9

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Daf 66 Marathon Coupe: A vivid Dutch DAF 66 - in daffodil yellow - lands at the North Yorkshire showroom. S7 Ep10

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Train Truckers

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Train Truckers
UAndYesterday.uk.description: 100 Ton Train: A fully restored Class 47 diesel engine is transported from its home at Crewe Heritage Centre in Cheshire to the Ecclesbourne Valley Railway in Derbyshire. S2 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.description: New. Paul and Suki negotiate their motorhome under a low bridge in the rain in the Lake District after having a cup of coffee. S1 Ep2

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Drama based on the true story of the largest uprising during the Holocaust. New arrivals at a Nazi concentration camp become involved in a bold scheme to break all 600 prisoners out.

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Simon looks back on wildlife stories he has discovered, from a giant tortoise sanctuary in the Seychelles to armed conservationists defending a forest in Belize. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Documentary going behind the scenes at the car company's plant as work gets underway on a range of 4x4s, from the factory floor to the world's most exclusive car showroom.

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Jaguar 2+2 E Type: Paul's on a big day out collecting a 1971 Jaguar E-Type and a 1933 Morgan 3-wheeler Supersport but first there's a flock of 300 chickens to negotiate before he can load up. S7 Ep11

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
